<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HE IS MY SAVIOR</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa thisan lul apawt,
 Ka bat takna dingin;
 A lu thiengtho chuh a khun a,
 Hinna ka muhtheih nan.

[V2]
 Belam No nunnempen chun,
 Kalvari-ah A thuok;
 Belam No thahsa hung thokitpa chuh,
 Ka Hukdampa ahi.

[V3]
 2. Ka thil hihkhelhte haw ziekin,
 Kross chungah Amau a;
 Lungsietna leh hehpih vangin,
 Ei piei kumsawt hinna.

[V4]
 3. Nisa'n A mel a selgu a,
 A vak a suoh ngam puoi;
 Hukdampa'n ka gitloh puo a,
 Kross-a A thawk laikhan.

[V5]
 4. Kenle ka lu khun ingka ting,
 Lalpa kross ma a chun;
 A thawknat zie ngaihtuoh ingka,
 A meltak ka muh chun.

[V6]
 5. Ka lungngaih luonthi luong mahleh,
 Kei di'n A thuok na zawi;
 Ka pumin kipie mai ingka,
 Zie mai chu ka theih tawp.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>125</hymn_number>
</song>